口述实录 | 疫情发生后，我们想到要解决“口罩脸”“酒精手”的问题。
At the time of the outbreak, we thought of dealing with Mask Face and Alcohol Hands.
陈涓玲 沈 林。
Chen Juan Ling Shen Lin.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
