目前为止，伽蓝已累计捐款捐物超过1000万元，全国近2万名医护人员用上了伽蓝的产品，我们感到非常自豪，能够为一线医护人员尽一些绵薄之力。
So far, gamma has donated more than 10 million yuan, and nearly 20,000 medical workers across the country have used gamma products. We are very proud to be able to do something for front-line medical workers.
口述 | 陈涓玲整理 | 沈  林最近的一个多月以来，每天从早到晚都在忙忙碌碌中，处理着在疫情之下公司的内外部沟通，好久没有睡过一个完整的觉了。
Chen Jianling has been busy from morning to night at night, dealing with the company's internal and external communications under the epidemic for over a month now. He has not slept a whole night.
我是伽蓝集团的公关传播总经理陈涓玲，大家可能对于我们旗下的化妆品品牌更为熟知，自然堂、美素、春夏、植物智慧、珀芙研、COMO等等。
I am Chen Tian Ling, general manager of communications at Gambari Group. You may be more familiar with our cosmetics brand, such as Nature Hall, Maxine, Spring and Summer, Plant Wisdom, Pepper Research, COMO, etc.
虽然我们无法像白衣天使那样，直接奔赴一线救死扶伤，但疫情发生到现在的每一天里，从集团董事长郑春颖先生到管理团队一直在想，作为中国化妆品领军企业，我们能做些什么来履行更多的责任和担当。
Although we can't go directly to the front line to save lives, as the angel of white, but every day from the group's chairman, Mr. Cheng Chunying to the management team, we have been wondering what we can do as a leader in Chinese cosmetics to take on more responsibilities and responsibilities.
时间拨回到1月20日，我们看到消息，武汉发生的新型冠状病毒肺炎存在人传人的情况，专家建议大家戴好口罩。
Back to January 20, we saw news, Wuhan occurred in the new coronavirus pneumonia human-to-human transmission of the situation, experts recommend that we wear a mask.
因为公司是1月22日开始春节放假，所以第一时间采购了1000只KN95口罩，发放给过年返乡的同事。
As the company started the Spring Festival holiday on January 22, the first time to purchase 1000 KN95 masks, distributed to returning colleagues.
同时我们也向口罩厂预定了200万元的订单，打算捐赠到抗疫一线，以及我们的员工和员工的家属，还有我们的合作伙伴。
We also placed a $2 million order with the mask factory to donate to the frontline of the epidemic, as well as to the families of our staff and staff, and our partners.
没想到两天后厂家告诉我们：口罩厂被政府征用了，物资优先供给医疗一线。
Unexpectedly, two days later the manufacturers told us: the mask factory was requisitioned by the Government, priority supplies of medical first line.
听到这个消息，我们非常理解和支持，也想到国内采购医疗物资肯定比较困难，于是紧急联系了我们在海外的同事帮忙协调，做全球范围的物资采购。
At this news, we understand and support, and also think that the domestic procurement of medical supplies will be more difficult, so we contacted our overseas colleagues to help coordinate the global procurement of materials.
公司也在1月23日成立了“伽蓝疫情防控应急小组”，要求所有员工每天更新健康状况，并从海外采购针对病情有疗效的药品作为储备给到有需要的员工们。
On January 23, the company established the "Emergency Response Team for the Prevention and Control of the Gamma Outbreak," which requires all employees to update their health on a daily basis and procure effective drugs from overseas as a reserve for those in need.
我们旗下的专业功效性护肤品牌珀芙研与医院的联系十分密切。
Our professional efficacy of the skin care products brand Puerver Research and the hospital is very closely linked.
在1月25日（大年初一）的时候，关于武汉新型冠状病毒肺炎的新闻越来越多，尤其是武汉协和医院的物资严重短缺，我们立即做出反应第一时间捐赠了2000只口罩，直接寄达医院，同时寄送了1000只口罩给公司湖北一线的美容顾问员工，虽然数量不多，但已竭尽所能。
On January 25 (New Year's Day), Wuhan on the new coronavirus pneumonia more and more news, especially Wuhan Concoronavirus Hospital material shortages, we immediately donated 2, 000 masks, sent directly to the hospital, and sent 1000 masks to the company's Hubei line beauty consultant staff, although the number is small, has done everything possible.
1月28日，疫情防控的形势愈发严峻，我们紧急协调联系了官方指定机构武汉红十字会，捐赠了500万元现金，希望能为抗疫做一点贡献。
On January 28, the situation of epidemic prevention and control became more serious. We contacted the Wuhan Red Cross, the official designated agency, and donated 5 million yuan in cash in the hope of contributing to the fight against the disease.
随着疫情的暴发，集团了解到上海本地的一些医院物资也很紧缺，于是捐赠了5000只KN95口罩给上海瑞金医院。
As the outbreak unfolded, the group learned that some local hospitals in Shanghai were in short supply, and donated 5,000 KN95 masks to the Shanghai Ruijin Hospital.
此外，伽蓝还捐赠了3000只口罩给上海市奉贤区金汇镇和四团镇，并陆续为奉贤区全区收治点、医院发热门诊、社区隔离点等共600位一线医护人员捐赠1200支珀芙研728霜和3000支自然堂护手霜，寄送2000只KN95口罩和200瓶珀芙研728霜给武汉及各地一线后勤保障人员。
In addition, Ga Lan donated 3,000 masks to Jinhui Town and Four Troupe Township in Fengxian District of Shanghai, and donated 1,200 Peifeng 728 creams and 3,000 nature paraphernalia to 600 frontline medical workers in Fengxian district, hospital heating clinics and community isolation points, and sent 2,000 KN95 masks and 200 bottles of Peifu 728 cream to frontline logistics personnel in Wuhan and other places.
同时，我们还注意到，因为长期佩戴口罩，医生护士们出现了“口罩脸”——长时间佩戴口罩，会让皮肤闷热不透气，容易滋生细菌，也容易使脸颊、鼻翼、耳后发生压力性损伤，而且有的口罩面料会产生一些游离甲醛，导致皮肤过敏。
At the same time, we have noticed that doctors and nurses wear masks for a long period of time, which makes the skin stuffy and stuffy, easy to grow bacteria, and prone to stress damage on the cheeks, nose and back of the ears. Some mask fabrics produce some free formaldehyde, leading to skin allergies.
针对口罩中成分致敏的情况，珀芙研728霜里面的舒缓成分西藏温泉水和马齿苋，能够有效缓解皮肤的敏感反应，改善口罩致敏引发的面部瘙痒、红肿等不适感。
The soothing ingredients in the mask's 728 cream, warm spring water and purslane, are effective in relieving the skin's sensitive reactions and improving the sensitivity of the facial itching and swelling caused by the mask.
而产品中还添加了深层保湿成分牛油果树果脂，防止口罩部位皮肤在水分蒸发后出现干燥脱屑。
The product also added deep moisturizing ingredients shea butter fruit resin, to prevent the mask parts of the skin after evaporation drying desquamate.
我们想，这不正是珀芙研728霜最擅长解决的肌肤敏感问题吗？于是，珀芙研品牌从2月1日开始，将各地销售的产品陆续捐赠给26个省的144家医院及3支医疗队，一共捐赠了大约价值331万元的珀芙研728霜，缓解12608人员的“口罩脸”问题。
Since February 1, Pearl Research has donated products from all over the world to 144 hospitals and 3 medical teams in 26 provinces, donating a total of about 3.31 million yuan of Puff Research 728 cream to ease the facial mask problem of 12,608 personnel.
后来，人民日报也发现了“口罩脸”这一现象，专门发了一组名为《脸》的微信图片新闻，引起了大家的广泛关注，也因此影响更多的护肤品牌针对医护人员“口罩脸”开始加入爱心捐赠行列。
"People's Daily later found the phenomenon of face masks, a group of micro-photos named" face "has attracted a lot of attention, and therefore more skin-care brand" mask face "for medical personnel began to join the ranks of charity donation.
2月9日，我们关注到武汉汉口医院的工作人员在微博上发了求助信息，说医院的年轻护士们急缺护手霜。
On February 9, we noticed that the staff of Hankou Hospital in Wuhan posted a message of help on Weibo, saying that young nurses in the hospital were in urgent need of hand cream.
原来，因为每天频繁使用消毒液、洗手液，奋战在一线的白衣天使们的手部出现了湿疹、脱皮、皲裂等现象。
It turns out that because of frequent use of disinfectant and hand sanitizer every day, the hands of the white-clad angels fighting on the front line have eczema, peeling, chapping and so on.
看到这个消息以后我们很心疼，第二天就请武汉的同事联系了医院，将整个武汉地区的自然堂和春夏两个品牌的5000支护手霜全部调拨在一起，由伽蓝的员工亲自送到了汉口医院。
Seeing this news, we were very distressed, the next day asked Wuhan colleagues to contact the hospital, the whole Wuhan area of the natural and spring and summer brands of 5000 hand cream were transferred to Hankou Hospital in person by the staff of gamma blue.
自然堂的护手霜含有珍贵玫瑰果油成分、春夏护手霜含有乳木果油成分，都可以有效帮助医护人员应对“酒精手”这个现象。
Nature Hall's hand cream contains precious components of rose oil, spring and summer hand cream contain shea butter ingredients, can effectively help health care workers deal with the phenomenon of "alcohol hand."
同时，我们还从上海的大仓调货，约有两万五千多支的护手霜，分别送到了武汉的汉口医院、金银潭医院、宜昌市夷陵医院、宜昌中心医院、宜昌第一人民医院，同济医院，北京大学人民医院医疗队、上海援鄂医疗队等。
At the same time, we also transferred some 25,000 hand cream from the warehouse in Shanghai to Hankou Hospital, Gold and Silver Pool Hospital, Yichang City Yiling Hospital, Yichang Central Hospital, Yichang First People's Hospital, Tongji Hospital, Peking University People's Hospital Medical Team, and Hubei Medical Team.
以上的这些事，其实挺平凡的，都是我们尽我们所能而已，后来央视新闻联播和新闻直播间连续报道了我们的爱心公益行动之后，公司又收到了不同渠道的很多求助信息，我们也意识到越来越多的地方需要这些物资，所以后续也对接了更多的医疗队和抗疫一线的工作人员进行了“口罩脸”、“酒精手”的捐赠。
After CCTV's CCTV news network and news station reported on our charity work, the company received a lot of help from different sources, and we realized that more and more places needed these materials, so more medical teams and frontline staff donated masks and alcohol hands.
目前为止，伽蓝已累计捐款捐物超过1000万元，全国近2万名医护人员用上了伽蓝的产品，我们感到非常自豪，能够为一线医护人员尽一些绵薄之力。
So far, gamma has donated more than 10 million yuan, and nearly 20,000 medical workers across the country have used gamma products. We are very proud to be able to do something for front-line medical workers.
同时，我们也响应国家和政府号召，推迟了原本的复工时间，从2月3日调整到2月10日。
At the same time, we also responded to calls from the State and the Government to postpone the original resumption of work from 3 February to 10 February.
伽蓝工厂开工日的复工率和复产率都较低，因为很多外地回沪的员工必须先居家隔离14天， 所以为了增加产能，我们也想了一些方法，其中就包括“共享员工”计划。
The restart and reactivation rates for the gamma plant are low, as many expatriates have to stay at home for 14 days before returning to Shanghai, so we've come up with a number of ways to increase capacity, including a "share staff" program.
伽蓝的厂区在上海奉贤，我们也是东方美谷的代表企业，所以当我们将需求向区委区政府提报申请了以后，区里第一时间响应帮助我们协调了一些园区内的其他餐饮、养老企业来我们厂区上班，艰难时刻，不同行业互相取暖，我们感到很开心。
Since we applied to the district government, the district first-time response helped us coordinate the work of some other catering and old-age enterprises in our factory district. We felt very happy about the difficult times and the different industries heating each other.
2月12日，伽蓝工厂迎来了24位餐饮员工的“增援”，（均未离沪或已满14天隔离期）经培训后作为车间一线操作人员，工资由伽蓝承担。
February 12, the gamma plant welcomed 24 catering staff "reinforcements" (neither from Shanghai or has completed the 14-day isolation period) after training as a front-line operator in the workshop, with wages borne by gamma blue.
“增援”的加入让我们从原先的2条生产线拓展到4条生产线，复工第一周产能增加了28%。
The addition of reinforcements has allowed us to expand from two production lines to four, increasing capacity by 28 per cent in the first week of operation.
但在人员还是有限的情况下，我们也是集中力量在最需要的产品上，主要做珀芙研728霜和护手霜的生产。
But with limited staff, we also focused on the most needed products, mainly to do the Pepperfield 728 cream and hand cream production.
在最近的一段时间，第二批的共享员工也已经到岗，我们与一家护理院合作，聘用其护理人员分别去到我们的产线与物流岗位，累计共享员工人数已达119人。
Recently, a second batch of shared staff has arrived, and we have worked with a nursing home to hire nursing staff to our production and logistics posts, bringing the total number of shared staff to 119.
此外，我们判断疫情期间，社会对于消毒杀菌类的产品需求量将变得很大。
In addition, we judge that during the epidemic, the social demand for sterilization products will become very large.
事实也是如此，专家在新闻报道里建议大家做好消毒杀菌工作后，相关的一些含有酒精等添加成分的消毒和洗手液，在局部地区出现了产品脱销短缺的现象。
In fact, experts in the news report that we have to do a good job of sterilization, some of the alcohol-containing components of disinfection and hand sanitizer, in local areas there is a shortage of products.
因此，我们决定旗下的自然堂、春夏、珀芙研3个品牌快速投产“消毒液”、“免洗消毒洗手液”、“卫生湿巾”共计10个产品，满足消费者的刚性需求，缓解社会压力。
Therefore, we have decided that three of our brands, namely Nature Hall, Spring and Summer, and Puff Research, will rapidly produce 10 products - disinfectant, disinfectant and sanitary towel - to meet the rigid demands of consumers and relieve social pressure.
其实伽蓝一直有在做消杀类产品的研发，但疫情的到来加速了新品上市的过程。
In fact, gamma blue has been doing research and development of sterilization products, but the arrival of the epidemic accelerated the process of new products on the market.
为了产品能够迅速上线，我们也跟生产伙伴做好协同，力争最短时间能够投入生产。
In order to be able to quickly go online, we also work with production partners, and strive to be able to enter production in the shortest possible time.
增加新的业务，这也算是我们企业渡过疫情难关的一种方式。
Adding new business is also a way for our company to weather the epidemic.
此前，伽蓝在19年的发展历史中，经历过2003年的非典，2008年、2012年的金融危机，但我们都挺过来了，这次疫情虽然会对经济产生影响，但我们会尽自己最大的努力去化解——一如既往为消费者提供优质的产品和服务，这也是我们紧急布局消杀类产品的初衷。
We have survived the SARS epidemic of 2003 and the financial crises of 2008 and 2012 in 19 years of development, but we have survived the epidemic and will do our best to defuse it - as always, to provide high-quality products and services to consumers, which is what our emergency layout has been designed to eliminate.
伽蓝的消杀类产品将在2月底陆续上市。
GRBS products will be on the market by the end of February.
作为中国本土的化妆品领军企业，伽蓝在疫情发生的近一个月里，虽然不能像医生护士那样冲在救助病患的第一线，但每一天我们都在积极组织复工复产，努力想办法为这场疫情阻击战和物资供应贡献我们的力量，风雨同舟，致敬所有"最美逆行者们"！征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
As a leading cosmetics company in China, while not on the frontline of care for patients during the past month of the epidemic, we have been actively organizing the resumption of work every day, trying to find a way to contribute to the epidemic's resistance and supplies.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
